---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Call Brad | Practical GDPR Compliance Solutions">

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="pt-32 pb-20 lg:pt-40 lg:pb-28 bg-gradient-to-br from-white via-gray-50 to-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-[#2b2e83]/5 rounded-full mb-6">
          <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-[#ed60ed] rounded-full align-middle"></span>
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-[#2b2e83] align-middle">GDPR Compliance Made Simple</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="font-montserrat text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-[#2b2e83] leading-tight mb-6">
          Practical GDPR products and support for teams that want a workable compliance setup without buying bloated enterprise tools
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-600 mb-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Call Brad helps startups and small-to-mid-sized businesses handle GDPR through a Notion-based workspace, employee training, and package-based DPO support that is clear, operational, and easy to maintain.
        </p>
        <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-500 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          The current launch format is built in Notion, so buyers can start with a practical workspace now and expand into broader privacy operations over time.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="https://calendar.notion.so/meet/javier-v1hzm20cy/callbrad-30" class="px-8 py-4 bg-[#2b2e83] text-white font-semibold rounded-xl hover:bg-[#232465] transition-all hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-[#2b2e83]/25">
            Book a call
          </a>
          <a href="#available-now" class="px-8 py-4 bg-white text-[#2b2e83] font-semibold rounded-xl border-2 border-[#2b2e83] hover:bg-[#2b2e83]/5 transition-colors">
            See what's available now
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Audience Section -->
  <section class="pb-20 lg:pb-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-3xl shadow-sm overflow-hidden">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_0.9fr]">
          <div class="p-8 sm:p-10 lg:p-12">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 bg-[#ed60ed]/10 rounded-full mb-5">
              <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#ed60ed]">Built for a specific buyer</span>
            </div>
            <h2 class="font-montserrat text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-[#2b2e83] mb-5">
              For teams that need GDPR to become manageable, not heavier
            </h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
              The offer is designed for startups and small-to-mid-sized businesses that need a practical GDPR setup without enterprise-software overhead or consultancy-heavy delivery.
            </p>
            <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
              <div class="rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 p-5">
                <h3 class="font-montserrat text-lg font-bold text-[#2b2e83] mb-2">Good fit</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">You want structure, visible ownership, and support your team can actually use day to day.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 p-5">
                <h3 class="font-montserrat text-lg font-bold text-[#2b2e83] mb-2">Current launch model</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">The workspace launches in Notion first, which keeps rollout simple while leaving room to grow beyond a narrow RoPA-only setup.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#2b2e83] to-[#232465] p-8 sm:p-10 lg:p-12 text-white">
            <h3 class="font-montserrat text-2xl font-bold mb-5">What you are actually buying</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-4 text-white/85">
              <li>One GDPR workspace that can hold records, review logic, follow-up work, and governance workflows.</li>
              <li>Training that can live alongside the rest of your operating setup instead of being bolted on elsewhere.</li>
              <li>DPO packages with clear monthly structure before you ever get on a call.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Available Now -->
  <section id="available-now" class="py-20 lg:py-28 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-montserrat text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-[#2b2e83] mb-4">
          What is available now
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          The current launch offer is broader than a RoPA tool. It includes a Notion-based GDPR workspace, employee training, and DPO support with visible package structure.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 justify-items-center">
        <!-- Workspace Card -->
        <a href="/ropa" class="group bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border-2 border-[#2b2e83]/20 hover:border-[#2b2e83] transition-all hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-[#2b2e83]/10 text-center">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#2b2e83] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform mx-auto">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-3 7h3m-3 4h3m-6-4h.01M9 16h.01"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-[#2b2e83]/70 mb-3">Available now in Notion</div>
          <h3 class="font-montserrat text-xl font-bold text-[#2b2e83] mb-3">GDPR Workspace</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">A Notion-based GDPR workspace for records, review logic, follow-up work, and broader privacy operations.</p>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center text-[#2b2e83] font-medium">
            Learn more
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </a>

        <!-- Training Card -->
        <a href="/training" class="group bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border-2 border-[#ed60ed]/40 hover:border-[#ed60ed] transition-all hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-[#ed60ed]/10 text-center">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-[#ed60ed] rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform mx-auto">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-[#ed60ed]/70 mb-3">Available now</div>
          <h3 class="font-montserrat text-xl font-bold text-[#ed60ed] mb-3">GDPR Training</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">A practical employee training offer that can be delivered alongside the rest of your operating setup.</p>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center text-[#ed60ed] font-medium">
            Learn more
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </a>

        <!-- DPO Card -->
        <a href="/dpo" class="group bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border-2 border-gray-200 hover:border-[#2b2e83]/50 transition-all hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-gray-200/50 text-center">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gray-700 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform mx-auto">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-gray-500 mb-3">Packages live now</div>
          <h3 class="font-montserrat text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">DPO Services</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Ongoing package-based support for businesses that need a designated and operationally useful DPO setup.</p>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center text-gray-700 font-medium">
            Learn more
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Workspace Section -->
  <section class="py-20 lg:py-28 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#2b2e83]/5 to-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center">
        <div>
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 bg-[#2b2e83]/10 rounded-full mb-6">
            <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#2b2e83]">Featured Product</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-montserrat text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-[#2b2e83] mb-6">
            A GDPR workspace that starts with RoPA and extends into the rest of compliance work
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
            The workspace starts in Notion because speed and usability matter. It gives teams a practical place to manage records of processing activities, related assessments, ownership, follow-up actions, and repeatable GDPR workflows without introducing a heavy software layer too early.
          </p>

          <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-[#2b2e83] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Collaborative and easier to maintain than static spreadsheets</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-[#2b2e83] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Broader than a narrow RoPA register because it supports the related work around it</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-[#2b2e83] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Launched in Notion now so teams can implement quickly and iterate without vendor bloat</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <a href="/ropa" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-[#2b2e83] text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-[#232465] transition-colors">
            Read more
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="relative">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-2xl shadow-[#2b2e83]/10 p-6 border border-gray-100">
            <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
              <img src="/imgs_callbrad/gdpr1.jpg" alt="RoPA Dashboard Preview" class="w-full h-auto" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 w-32 h-32 bg-[#ed60ed]/20 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 w-24 h-24 bg-[#2b2e83]/20 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Training Section -->
  <section class="py-20 lg:py-28 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center">
        <div class="relative order-2 lg:order-1">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-2xl shadow-[#ed60ed]/10 p-6 border border-gray-100">
            <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
              <img src="/imgs_callbrad/data211.jpg" alt="Training Platform Preview" class="w-full h-auto" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -left-4 w-32 h-32 bg-[#2b2e83]/20 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 w-24 h-24 bg-[#ed60ed]/20 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 bg-[#ed60ed]/10 rounded-full mb-6">
            <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#ed60ed]">Featured Product</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-montserrat text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-[#ed60ed] mb-6">
            GDPR training that lives where your team already works
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
            A practical way to train employees on GDPR without adding another separate training provider. Clear, easy to follow, and operationally useful with structured learning and proof of completion.
          </p>

          <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-[#ed60ed] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Clear employee GDPR training with practical business relevance</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-[#ed60ed] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Designed to be easy to deliver and easy to maintain</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-[#ed60ed] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-700">Proof of completion for audits</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <a href="/training" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-[#ed60ed] text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-[#d94dd9] transition-colors">
            Read more
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing Section -->
  <section id="pricing" class="py-20 lg:py-28 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-montserrat text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-[#2b2e83] mb-4">
          Pricing should be inspectable before the call
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          DPO packages are fixed and visible. The workspace and training offers are currently launch-stage and scoped with you, but the delivery format is clear now: the workspace launches in Notion and the support model is practical rather than consultancy-heavy.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-[1.15fr_0.85fr] gap-8 items-start">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-montserrat text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Essential DPO</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-5">For businesses that need a lean monthly structure.</p>
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#2b2e83] mb-5">€199<span class="text-lg text-gray-500 font-medium">/mo</span></div>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <li>1 x 30 min monthly sync call</li>
              <li>Yearly high-level GDPR gap analysis</li>
              <li>Basic email support</li>
              <li>Appointed DPO for 1 entity, 1 jurisdiction</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border-2 border-[#2b2e83] shadow-lg shadow-[#2b2e83]/10">
            <div class="inline-flex px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-[#2b2e83] text-white text-xs font-semibold mb-4">Most popular</div>
            <h3 class="font-montserrat text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Operational DPO</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-5">For active compliance needs and regular monthly work.</p>
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#2b2e83] mb-5">€599<span class="text-lg text-gray-500 font-medium">/mo</span></div>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <li>4 hours dedicated work/month</li>
              <li>1 x 30 min monthly sync call</li>
              <li>Yearly in-depth GDPR gap analysis</li>
              <li>Email and messaging support</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200">
            <h3 class="font-montserrat text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Growth DPO</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-5">For scaling teams that need priority support.</p>
            <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-[#2b2e83] mb-5">€999<span class="text-lg text-gray-500 font-medium">/mo</span></div>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <li>8 hours dedicated work/month</li>
              <li>2 x 30 min monthly sync calls</li>
              <li>Yearly in-depth analysis plus action plan</li>
              <li>Priority email, messaging, and phone support</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-[#2b2e83]/20">
            <div class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-[#2b2e83]/70 mb-3">Workspace launch format</div>
            <h3 class="font-montserrat text-2xl font-bold text-[#2b2e83] mb-3">GDPR Workspace</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Launched in Notion now so the implementation is faster and the scope can match your actual workflows.</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Pricing is currently scoped based on setup complexity, operating model, and rollout needs.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-[#ed60ed]/20">
            <div class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-[#ed60ed]/70 mb-3">Training launch format</div>
            <h3 class="font-montserrat text-2xl font-bold text-[#ed60ed] mb-3">GDPR Training</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Delivered as a practical training offer that can sit alongside your workspace and existing operating setup.</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Pricing is currently discussed based on team size, modules, and delivery requirements.</p>
          </div>

          <a href="/dpo" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 border-2 border-[#2b2e83] text-[#2b2e83] font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-[#2b2e83] hover:text-white transition-colors">
            Inspect full DPO pricing
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Section -->
  <section class="py-20 lg:py-28 bg-[#2b2e83] text-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-montserrat text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">
          A more workable way to handle GDPR
        </h2>
        <p class="text-white/80 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Many businesses end up choosing between expensive enterprise tools, external support that is too consultancy-heavy, or manual processes that become messy over time. Call Brad takes a more operational approach: launch in Notion where it is useful, make responsibilities visible, keep pricing legible, and avoid adding compliance theatre just to look sophisticated.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-montserrat text-xl font-bold mb-3">Practical, Not Theoretical</h3>
          <p class="text-white/70">Real-world solutions that fit how your business actually works, not textbook approaches.</p>
        </div>
